Description: 
    A modified and extended version of the 'lassosum' package tailored for modeling 
    multilocus risk scores (MRS) using MB-MDR-derived SNPâ€“SNP interaction statistics. 
    This pipeline enables soft-thresholding on F-statistics, risk score calculation 
    based on categorical interaction encoding (HLO), and model validation via 
    phenotype-stratified score distributions and ROC/AUC analysis.
